dct_title_s: Jan Mayen Island : to illustrate the paper by J. M. Wordie
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and hachures. Bays, capes, and coves are shown. Glaciers and elevation of Beerenberg are shown. From: Geographical journal. Vol. 59, no. 3 (March 1922), pp. 180-195; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6874
